causal_map:
Applying damping factor → Intervened transformed function; 
  Applying Laplace transform → Transformed function; 
  Operating with D(s) → Intervened transformed function; 
  Intervention (damping factor) → Original function; 
  Original function → Transformed function; 
  Transformed function → Inverse Laplace transform; 
  D(s) → Original differential operator; 
  Operating with D(s) → Intervened function in time domain; 
  Inverse Laplace transform → Function in time domain; 
  Intervened function in time domain → Resultant function in time domain; 
  Resultant function in time domain → Strictly follows the dynamics dictated by the original differential operator
